	<h1 class="title">全球最佳餐厅“全球巡演”，哥本哈根的那家店在干吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/113313/small/113313.jpg?1434099367" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马梦涵 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-11 08:55:32 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23662/medium/23662.jpg?1457627671" alt="" />			
	</div>
